verbose_text: The aim of this study was to investigate the changes in the expression of TJ associated proteins in the RPE - choroid complex in the eyes of guinea pigs with lens induced myopia (LIM), and to investigate the effect of RA on the TJs of the RPE - choroid complex of guinea pigs in vivo.
